<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Unsuccessful Course Completion</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
        }

        .logo-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 40%;
            height: 40%;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .company-info {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .company-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .company-tagline {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .violation-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .warning-icon {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid red;
            color: red;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-right: 8px;
            vertical-align: middle;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .violation-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .greeting {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .message-text {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .view-button {
            background-color: #17a2b8;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .view-button:hover {
            background-color: #138496;
        }

        .support-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .support-link {
            color: #17a2b8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .support-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer {
                background-color: #f8f9fa;
                padding: 15px 20px;
                border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
                font-size: 11px;
                color: #666;
                line-height: 1.4;
            }

            .footer-link {
                color: #17a2b8;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .footer-link:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header with Logo -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-section">
                <img src="https://proctoring-client-uploads-west.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/assets/bis-logo.png"
                    alt="BIS Logo" class="logo">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <!-- Violation Header -->
            <div class="violation-header">
                <table style="display:inline-block; vertical-align:middle; margin-right:8px;" cellpadding="0"
                    cellspacing="0">
                    <tr>
                        <td
                            style="width:20px; height:20px; border:2px solid red; border-radius:50%; text-align:center; font-size:14px; line-height:16px; color:red;">
                            &#33;
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <h2 class="violation-title">Manual Proctor Verification Required</h2>
            </div>


            <!-- Email Content -->
            <p class="greeting">Hello,</p>


            <p class="message-text">The virtual proctor could not verify the identity of
                <strong>{{participant_name}}</strong> with the government-issued photo ID they provided.
                They continued to take the online course <strong>{{course_name}}</strong> on <strong>{{date}}</strong>.
                Please verify the participant’s identity immediately. Their course status will remain pending until your
                manual verification is complete.
            </p>

            <p> Thanks kindly,<br />BIS Safety Software</p>

            <!-- Support Information -->
            <div class="support-info">
                <p>
                    If you do not believe these violations are valid or if you have any questions, please
                    contact the Support Team by phoning 1-866-416-1660 or emailing
                    <a href="mailto:{{supportMail}}" class="support-link">{{supportMail}}</a>.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    Thanks kindly!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                If you have any questions or believe you received this email in error, please contact our Support Team
                by phone at 1-866-416-1660
                or by email at <a href="mailto:{{supportMail}}" class="footer-link">{{supportMail}}</a>.
            </p>

            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                BIS Safety Software | 261 Seneca Road, Sherwood Park AB T8A 4G6, Canada<br>
                <a href="{{termsUrl}}" class="footer-link">Terms and Conditions</a> |
                <a href="{{privacyUrl}}" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a>
            </p>

            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                This is an automated email message. Please do not reply to this email address.
            </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>